{"tid":1266650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人要係捱到七一先完，我係要你堅持到2047！","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:00:34.000Z","uid":143210,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1169b69026a715ff51e9c8553174940827ea163","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"我諗大家都太睇重呢次g20同反送中了<br />\n<br />\n我明機會難得，但唔代表日日出成效就會大過一星期一次動員，因為唔係個個學生都畀得起四十蚊來回去日日撐場<br />\n<br />\n我立此存證，七一後政府一定毫不退讓，九月後我地情況只會更加嚴竣<br />\n<br />\n辱警法，監控，濫權，私隱問題，暴動定性案例<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">從今以後抗爭城本係會節節上升</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，上唔到枱面，就要落枱底，你只會愈來愈易犯惡法<br />\n唔係日日出街先叫做到啲咩，而係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集體出動，分散準備</span><br />\n<br />\n文宣資源就係分散嘅後援<br />\n集體出動係提供人數保勇派安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要義士不撤控，你就係暴徒一員，不要再置身事外</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而家遠遠未係革命，喺度唱do you hear the people sing，無準備唱呢首你係咪想人笑大個口？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人憑咩遊行一個月就可以得到民主</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地想留喺香港嘅話，就要做好抗爭嘅心理準備，唔好再話攰了想死，而係要令自己可以避過極權追捕，堅持到最後！"},{"pid":"41ad602929204ab230ec5789ec49487621f27869","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"諗通就唔好再同我尋死<br />\n<br />\n我地要尋生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741891e8ee7ba41f93b4d7d8cd002364588df0a5","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"&mdash; 生 命 何 價 &mdash; 七一早上六點半灣仔修_球場見 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266641</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ccace36b047372084295553970a80f946803353","tid":1266650,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n戰到2047"},{"pid":"179b394c25ebbd6557d441bbb72e58b48c6d599f","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ccace36b047372084295553970a80f946803353","tid":1266650,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n戰到2047"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"不要被捕，不要死<br />\n<br />\n做好準備"},{"pid":"a0e7627892a261d93605f46448bb220785479cc6","tid":1266650,"uid":76395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:30:13.000Z","msg":"推左先講"},{"pid":"54abfdbe2e7392d5978dc561bdd8f612304703ef","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"請大家唔好再散播失敗主義，因為我地仍然有好多嘢要做，例如輿論戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241097</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c78cf2ac68e532b46d3d88771c3ce80a3dab209","tid":1266650,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a46717e2570e39bba9a275e853c9ecbdc413ad08","tid":1266650,"uid":95757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，隨左現時抗爭，重有其他事可以做<br />\n<br />\n致想自殺既反送中人士......遊行、示威、不合作運動既下步！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"562f98cc8dc609d4c0da8eda8fa4d360328810ce","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"如果反對即暴動<br />\n<br />\n我願<br />\n<br />\n人地暴動但拉我地<br />\n<br />\n我不甘"},{"pid":"b1e4fce1fe23bb186a9f34c2b5f449df4ad43f90","tid":1266650,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b833db8df9a23a79faee403e66eb799008b4ac","tid":1266650,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:44:32